Platform services and hosting
These services have the purpose of hosting and running key components of Blackjack Apprenticeship, therefore allowing the provision of Blackjack Apprenticeship from within a unified platform. Such platforms provide a wide range of tools to the Owner – e.g. analytics, user registration, commenting, database management, e-commerce, payment processing – that imply the collection and handling of Personal Data. Some of these services work through geographically distributed servers, making it difficult to determine the actual location where the Personal Data are stored.
Shopify (Shopify Inc.)
