F. Authorized Agent
You may authorize an agent to take any of the acts permitted in this Section VII on your behalf. To do so, you must provide written and signed authority to the agent, and written and signed notice to Wistia that Wistia may act on such requests by that agent.
G. Requests Regarding Media
Wistia does not collect, process, use, disclose, share, or sell Personal Information from the Media created and distributed by our Customers,
e.g.
, images, voice recordings, etc. If you have any questions regarding the Personal Information contained in particular Media, please contact the party that created or distributed that Media.
